---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | Pouria Alaei"
  description="About Pouria Alaei, Senior Embedded Software Engineer focused on Embedded Linux, Edge AI, and hardware/software integration."
>
  <main class="page">
    <section class="section intro">
      <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
      <h1>Engineering systems from hardware to software.</h1>

      <p class="lead">
        I am a Senior Embedded Software Engineer focused on building practical,
        production-ready systems that connect embedded software, electronics,
        Linux, connectivity, and intelligent edge applications.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="content-grid">
      <article class="card">
        <h2>What I Do</h2>
        <p>
          I work across the full embedded product stack: hardware bring-up,
          firmware, Embedded Linux, Qt-based HMI, backend services, networking,
          communication protocols, and system-level integration.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <h2>Engineering Focus</h2>
        <p>
          My work is strongest where software and hardware meet: industrial
          devices, IoT systems, edge AI applications, Linux-based embedded
          platforms, and products that need reliable real-world operation.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <h2>Leadership</h2>
        <p>
          I have experience leading technical work, coordinating hardware and
          software decisions, reviewing implementation risks, and turning
          product requirements into practical engineering plans.
        </p>
      </article>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .eyebrow {
    color: #67e8f9;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  h1 {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 12px 0 0;
    font-size: clamp(42px, 7vw, 72px);
    line-height: 1.05;
  }

  .lead {
    max-width: 760px;
    color: #cbd5e1;
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 18px;
    padding-bottom: 80px;
  }

  h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
    color: #93c5fd;
  }

  p {
    color: #cbd5e1;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
</style>
